import Foundation
import Specta

func scrapeWebpage(_ urlString: String) -> [String] {
    guard let url = URL(string: urlString),
          let response = try? URLRequest(url: url),
          let htmlData = try? Data(contentsOf: response) else {
        fatalError("Failed to load webpage")
    }
    
    // Parse HTML using Specta
    do {
        let parsedHtml = try Specta.parse(htmlData)
        
        // Extract all paragraph texts
        var paragraphs = Array<String>()
        for element in parsedHtml["body"]!["p"]! {
            paragraphs.append(element["text"]!)
        }
        
        return paragraphs
    } catch {
        fatalError("Failed to parse HTML")
    }
}

let urlString = "https://example.com"
if let results = scrapeWebpage(urlString) {
    print(results)
}
```
